INSTALLATION:

    sudo apt-get -y install libpqxx-dev

POSTGRES:

    In order to enter the psql terminal, type "psql" into the terminal

    In order to view the test table, type "select * from test;"


Scraper:

    In order to run the code, change to the code's directory and type:
        "g++ main.cpp -o test -lpqxx -lpq"

    Then type:
        "./test"



credit to https://www.jeremymorgan.com/tutorials/c-programming/how-to-capture-the-output-of-a-linux-command-in-c/
for the function that captures the output from a given terminal command